    • Method Detail

      • getBrightness

        public float getBrightness()
        Indicates how well the face is lit for purposes of analysis. Value range is [0, 100]. There are no hard boundaries, but consider the following ranges as general guidelines:
        0-10: too dark
        10-25: suboptimal
        25-75: well lit
        75-90: suboptimal
        90-100: too bright
